headline: Is Paychex Offering Value After an 18.9% Slide Amid HR Tech Competition?
summary: If you are wondering whether Paychex at around $112 a share is a bargain or a trap, you are not alone. This article is going to unpack what that price really implies. The stock has slipped about 2.7% over the last week and is down 18.9% year to date, but longer term holders are still sitting on gains of roughly 36.5% over five years.
